Touch Screen
============

|product| is equipped with a multi-point capacitive touch screen. Its multi-point touch detection capability enables implementation of some advanced GUI operations,
such as two-finger zoom or rotation. 

The capacitive touch screen can be operated by fingers, gloves with a special coating, or a conductive stylus.

.. container:: hatnote hatnote-yellow

  | **Size/Type:** |dispsize| multi-point capacitive touch screen
  | **Surface Hardness:** 7H
  | **Service Life (MTBF):** 50 million touch events
  | **Light Transmittance:** > 92%